{"tid":2111494,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10.1衝突 警作供多次要求看記事冊 稱遭文員撞倒 「睄到有個黑色身影」","createTime":"2020-07-16T14:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T15:58:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f114deefa4f6cc92884ab629e67107b39fe9a99b","tid":2111494,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075563&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=c98c93c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075563&h=7113cd7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075563</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）10月1日有多區發起遊行示威，及後引發警民衝突，多人被捕。一名29歲文員在銅鑼灣被指撞到警員，早前否認一項襲警罪。案件今日（16日）在東區裁判法院開審，報稱被撞的督察林泰金甫作供即多次要求翻看記事冊喚起記憶，又指被撞後擰轉頭「餘光睄到有個黑色身影」，此時被告身在附近，故認為他是施襲者。"},{"pid":"8d3487e53b7ab5adaaf265133bed0e577361487c","tid":2111494,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"林督察稱，其後以自己190磅的身體壓著被告以制服，被告曾掙扎想走，但承認辯方所指「唔知佢係咪痛所以先郁」，小隊傳令員16869隨後協助制服。作出拘捕後，林發現著短褲的被告雙膝擦傷流血，於是為他安排急救人員。<strong><span class=\"red\">林又稱，當日在律敦治醫院接受治理後即日出院，並獲發7日病假，並形容左背有酸痛，「唔知拉親定咩」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b8b349aa9148f6fb92aa52e4da3e9dfc5afb17","tid":2111494,"uid":189523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"黑色身影？速狗？"},{"pid":"7eec16e9680ead55fff38cc91c7808e30ef46fe7","tid":2111494,"uid":21545